+// ── PUCT constant ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+// PUCT = Q(s,a) + c_puct * P(a|s) * sqrt(N) / (1 + n_a)
+//
+// AlphaGo uses c_puct = 5.0 for large networks.  Our computed prior is weaker
+// than a trained policy network, so we use a smaller c_puct = 2.0 to avoid
